731/******************************************************************************/

733/* Analog to Digital Converter */

737/******************** Bit definition for ADC_SR register ********************/
738#define ADC_SR_AWD_Pos (0U)
739#define ADC_SR_AWD_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_AWD_Pos)
740#define ADC_SR_AWD ADC_SR_AWD_Msk
741#define ADC_SR_EOC_Pos (1U)
742#define ADC_SR_EOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_EOC_Pos)
743#define ADC_SR_EOC ADC_SR_EOC_Msk
744#define ADC_SR_JEOC_Pos (2U)
745#define ADC_SR_JEOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_JEOC_Pos)
746#define ADC_SR_JEOC ADC_SR_JEOC_Msk
747#define ADC_SR_JSTRT_Pos (3U)
748#define ADC_SR_JSTRT_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_JSTRT_Pos)
749#define ADC_SR_JSTRT ADC_SR_JSTRT_Msk
750#define ADC_SR_STRT_Pos (4U)
751#define ADC_SR_STRT_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_STRT_Pos)
752#define ADC_SR_STRT ADC_SR_STRT_Msk
753#define ADC_SR_OVR_Pos (5U)
754#define ADC_SR_OVR_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_SR_OVR_Pos)
755#define ADC_SR_OVR ADC_SR_OVR_Msk
757/******************* Bit definition for ADC_CR1 register ********************/
758#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos (0U)
759#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Msk (0x1FUL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
760#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Msk
761#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_0 (0x01UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
762#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_1 (0x02UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
763#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_2 (0x04UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
764#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_3 (0x08UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
765#define ADC_CR1_AWDCH_4 (0x10UL << ADC_CR1_AWDCH_Pos)
766#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Pos (5U)
767#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Pos)
768#define ADC_CR1_EOCIE ADC_CR1_EOCIE_Msk
